    lead: "These are public-site observations, not private analytics claims. They matter because paid and organic traffic both depend on clear page hierarchy, clean indexation, and strong commercial paths.",
    layout: "cards",
    chips: ["Duplicate H1s", "Sitemap review", "Hierarchy", "Source tracking"],
    note: "Public observations only",
